com.pilot.jword
Class PageSize

java.lang.Object
  com.pilot.jword.PageSize

public class PageSize
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a single page type. Keeps pages size and identification. Standard page sizes are also defined as static values. This class defined standard metrics (in twips) for a page type, irrelevant from orientation, margins or column format.
